The answer was found in the provided sources. According to [1], chunk_001298, a self-employed individual must consider the prihodki (revenues) and odhodki (expenses) for the tax base. These revenues and expenses are determined in accordance with the laws and accounting standards specified in the ZDavP-2 statute.

